{"tid":2123076,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"魏京生︰北京藉領館指揮諜戰","createTime":"2020-07-24T11:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T11:28:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6074e30b7733fe53a7eb4533ef5ce15c8cb42571","tid":2123076,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:28:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/WQLMCCXRZUKOZ5KOZM7AHWXUZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FWQLMCCXRZUKOZ5KOZM7AHWXUZQ%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxSfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=44024789\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FWQLMCCXRZUKOZ5KOZM7AHWXUZQ%2F&h=c3b3e3c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/WQLMCCXRZUKOZ5KOZM7AHWXUZQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n魏京生︰北京藉領館指揮諜戰<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國在美國五個城市設有總領事館，美國為何選擇侯斯頓下手？流亡民運人士魏京生認為，這是因為當地是中國在美情報活動的指揮中心。在美國下令中國侯斯頓總領館關閉之前的一天，被控以簽證欺詐罪的中國訪問學者宋琛（Song Chen音譯）在聯邦地方法院首次出庭，控方並披露被告在上月曾從電腦外接硬盤刪除一封自己致中國駐紐約總領館的函件。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：英把關機制 或禁港警、公僕入籍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GTj75l94XCdvu0-ZFsDX9UIqS-4=/374x249/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ASGJMJDCRHZ5MIJAW372RUDMUU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGTj75l94XCdvu0-ZFsDX9UIqS-4%3D%2F374x249%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FASGJMJDCRHZ5MIJAW372RUDMUU.gif&h=d4ad7123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魏京生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑因涉欺詐華學者燒文件<br />\n<br />\n魏京生接受自由亞洲電台訪問時指，近期中國黑客間諜活動太過猖獗，令美國找到理由升級行動對付中國。他指美國國務卿蓬佩奧在擔任現職前為中央情報局局長，了解中共在美國的間諜活動，「所以這次要打就打蛇打七寸，就打你情報機關的指揮機構。」<br />\n<br />\n中國侯斯頓總領館在被美方下令關閉當晚，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其實，各國領事館一直都被指具收集情報功能，。。。。。。。。。。"}]}